</tr>
</table>
<ul>
<li><i>A Testament to Freedom: The Essential Writings of Dietrich Bonhoeffer</i> (1990). Geoffrey B. Kelly and F. Burton Nelson, editors. Harper SanFrancisco 1995 2nd edition, paperback: <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0060642149" class="internal">ISBN 0-06-064214-9</a></li>
</ul>
