<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Dietrich_Bonhoeffer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Opera">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Opera</span></h3>
<ul>
