<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Dietrich_Bonhoeffer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Art (Iconography)">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Art (Iconography)</span></h3>
