aw" title="Category:People from Wrocław">People from Wrocław</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Protestant_martyrs_of_Modern_Times" title="Category:Protestant martyrs of Modern Times">Protestant martyrs of Modern Times</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Protestant_victims_of_Nazism" title="Category:Protestant victims of Nazism">Protestant victims of Nazism</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Religious_workers_who_died_in_Nazi_concentration_camps" title="Category:Religious workers who died in Nazi concentration camps">Religious workers who died in Nazi concentration camps</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:German_Protestants_opposed_to_the_Third_Reich" title="Category:German Protestants opposed to the Third Reich">German Protestants opposed to the Third Reich</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Flossenb%C3%BCrg_concentration_camp_victims" title="Category:Flossenbürg concentration camp victims">Flossenbürg concentration camp victims</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:German_Lutherans" title="Category:German Lutherans">German Lutherans</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Christian_theologians" title="Category:Christian theologians">Christian theologians</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Christian_philosophers" title="Category:Christian philosophers">Christian philosophers</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Christian_Ethicists" title="Category:Christian Ethicists">Christian Ethicists</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Anglican_saints" title="Category:Anglican saints">Anglican saints</a></span></div><div id="mw-hidden-catlinks" class="mw-hidden-cats-hidden">Hidden categories:&#32;<span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_to_be_expanded_since_February_2008" title="Category:Articles to be expanded since February 2008">Articles to be expanded since February 2008</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><